data.description: OPEN HOUSE This Friday March 1st, Saturday and Sunday 1 -5 pm.  GREAT LOCATION in City of Windcrest. Easy access to freeways and central via transportation. Garden Home w/In-ground Pool located on a cul-de-sac with center park area. 3 large bedrooms!  Completely rehab house! New insulation and drywall throughout. Concrete slab was coated with dry lock (waterproof) coating as a preventative measure prior to all flooring installs. Water heater replaced fall of 2022. Water softener was replaced with Euro de-scaler.  DOWNSTAIRS is the 13' x17' Master bedroom with marble tile accent wall and pendant lights for reading. The 20' x 10' Master bathroom is called a "zero-entry" Shower with a unique look, two shower heads and glass tiled walls 20' high to skylight. Duel glass and granite vessel sinks. Two walk in closets. The Living room has high ceilings with a floor to ceiling fireplace!  A formal dining room has recessed lighting with dimmers and a mirrored wall. Kitchen has a bistro corner; plus an eating area; all new  appliances; copper sink; rolling kitchen island; granite countertops and 2 pantries. The 1/2 bath has a marble tile featured wall and a glass vessel sink, located from the utility room. There is an exit door located for convenient access to and from the swimming pool and the detached garage. Beautiful covered patio has ceiling fan with an entrance to the living room. The pool: Energy efficient pump; plumbed for solar heat; can be re-converted to salt water; filter system & sand replaced summer of 2023. Pool surface and coping refinished summer of 2023. Pool is approx. 20,000 gal.  UPSTAIRS are 2 bedrooms, a loft  with a wet bar and a full bath with entry from both the hall & bedroom.  This bathroom has a soaking tub for full body relaxation! It features a marble and glass tile waterfall design behind the soaking tub. The bedroom 23' x 11' with a walk in closet is suitable as a 2nd Master Bedroom.  Home has Upgraded spray in foam insulation with a tall attic space in one area of the attic to convert to a miscellaneous room or great space for lots of storage! Oasis type setting in backyard with lots of privacy. A beautiful garden view from the kitchen.  All garden beds and part of the front yard have rubber mulch.  The property has fruit trees: banana, lemon, lime and mandarin.  Exterior has security and accent lighting. The detached garage with entry from the alley, can be converted to an apartment, as there is a full 2nd floor!  This is a MUST SEE HOUSE!  SCHEDULE A SHOWING TODAY!
